name: Pink, Red, Brown
description: Artist: Vida V. | This composition contains three calligraphic pieces, for the Persian words for Pink, Red, and Brown. I created them in TwoToJazz on iPad, using multi-touch gestures; i.e., my thumb and index finger as the calligraphic brush. I then overlaid and mixed the images in other apps. As for the textures, I use multiple other TwoToJazz works of mine. TwoToJazz itself is developed by me. | Creation date: June 1sr, 2019
